item.content:encoded: [vc_row row_content_width="fullwidth"][vc_column][bulkgal_slider speed="500" timeout="4000" pager="yes" galleryid="249"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_content_width="contained"][vc_column width="1/1"][toranj_title style="two-line" heading="h1" title="Portfolio Item" title2="A Nice "][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_content_width="contained"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]Unique, Versatile, Elegant and Flexible were the sticky words in our mind during design and developing this template.  Toranj is trying to bring the combination of beauty and power to the table and it’s suitable for a wide range of applications. For Creative Portfolio, Photography, Videography, Digital Agency, Interior Design to Personal Blogging and Magazine and even Creative Corporate websites, Toranj has the features alongside a modern design. We tried to dig further in term of responsiveness and make it not only working in different devices but also looking like it has been specifically designed for those devices. Toranj also has true RTL support, means you will get an exact RTL version of the template with all dummy Persian contents. Dedicated support, we did our best but it’s not yet finished and we will support our customers all the way to that final smile of satisfaction. That’s it as they say “You can design and create, and build the most wonderful place in the world. But it takes people to make the dream a reality ”, so here is the Toranj people, hope you enjoy it.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][toranj_list_container border="yes" style="with-icon" iconstyle="simple"][toranj_list_item text="Customer: owwwlab" icon="fa-heart"][toranj_list_item text="Date: 2014" icon="fa-calendar"][/toranj_list_container][vc_empty_space height="32px"][vc_progress_bar values="90|Development,80|Design,70|Marketing" bgcolor="custom" custombgcolor="#3cc171" options="striped"][toranj_button text="Vie demo" style="toranj" size="large" icon_align="simple" btn_url="url:%23||" el_class="btn-block"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

We tried to dig further in term of responsiveness and make it not only working in different devices but also looking like it has been specifically designed for those devices. Toranj also has true RTL support, means you will get an exact RTL version of the template with all dummy Persian contents.
